with the National Performance Review principle of providing guiding principles rather than rigid rules. Hence,
we are revising the Policy Letter, in particular sections 8a and 8b, to reflect this new approach. Agencies are encouraged
to begin developing implementation strategies and initiating staff training to ensure effective implementation
of the provisions of this revised Policy Letter until the Federal Acquisition Regulation (FAR) is changed.

Since the December 2, 1993 

Federal Register

 notice which also included the rescission of OMB Circular No. A-120, some agencies have raised concerns that
